leaders.name: Emil
leaders.description: Emil is the big brother of the group as he is the oldest among us and takes initiative in leading the team. He also has the most experience in entrepreneurship, having taken a gap year to do entre in China.

leaders.name: Kai Jie
leaders.description: The designer of the group along with Jo wee. 100% A++ aesthetics and makes sure everything is presentable. Also have good ideas and we all wished that there was more of him.

leaders.name: Jo Wee
leaders.description: Part 2 of the designers group with Kai jie, both of them have made Remoree the beautiful chair it is today. Is the logical voice of the group and always pulls us back if we wonder too far.

leaders.name: Daniel
leaders.description: funkiest guy in sutd and he is a nice guy but doesnt like to be called a nice guy because he thinks that is a boring defining feature. He helps bring the remoree chair to life along with the other epd kids, making sure its comfortable, lasting and the sensors work to give accurate feedback.

leaders.name: Timothy
leaders.description: another funky guy who is the time keeper of the group. He's a very responsible and hardworking guy that drives the team to our goals. He also has funny memes that really that fuels the soul of the group.

leaders.name: Yi Xuan
leaders.description: Yi Xuan is not all muscles, he is planning to go into computer engineering and will be contributing to the ISTD component of the group while helping out his fellow epd groupmates. He also has a unique sense of humour that either sends you rolling on the floor laughing or nevermind.
